name: HUGE ANTONOV 124 VISITS CALGARY! Antonov Airlines An-124-100 [4K]
description:
On June 26th, this Antonov 124 from Antonov Airlines flew into Calgary from Anchorage, Alaska, and left the following day for Goose Bay.

I’m not 100% sure what was on board, and they didn’t seem to load or offload anything. Still though, it was so nice to see one of these incredible Ukrainian planes in action again, especially one from Antonov themselves.

Слава Україні!
